Powering People‑Based Marketing Across the Open Web

People first, reaching every digitally addressable adult across every device,
screen and household on the open web.

   Learn More

Introducing OpenAudience™

OpenAudience is the people-based marketing platform for the open web. The
first of its kind capability to unlock walled garden advertising efficiency
and ease across the entirety of the open web has been engineered around three
core pillars:

   - Homepage

Privacy

   A platform built on privacy by design principles.
   - Homepage

Knowledge

   Unify data with unparalleled accuracy and precision. Unlock true
   knowledge about your customers or your audience.
   - Homepage

Performance

   Drive superior advertising performance and increase yield. All across
   the massive scale of the open web.

   - Homepage

Nobody understands the
open web better than OpenX

   With 10+ years running the industry’s largest and highest quality
   independent ad exchange, OpenX has unparalleled reach and scale across
   the open web.
