2019 Consumer Holiday Shopping Report

   In collaboration with The Harris Poll, OpenX conducted a nationwide
   study looking at consumer shopping ahead of the 2019 holiday season.
   The full study contains information on topics such as how much
   consumers are planning on spending this year, consumer views on Black
   Friday and more. Download the full report for more insights.
